    "The web page provides the vision and mission of the AI at Harvard program, which aims to foster collaboration and innovation in AI across the university.",
    "AI leaders and partners at Harvard can post their research on generative models.",
    "Through its website it showcases AI projects and research conducted by Harvard faculty and students, as well as AI tools and platforms available for the Harvard community.",
